title: 37. The 10 Things I Learned About Self Love this Decade
description:
Hey girl hey!

In this episode, I go over the 10 things I learned about self love this decade. You are not going to want to miss this episode! It is filled with so many gems that you can take with you to 2020 and reflect on as you head into the new year! 

Cheers to the New Year!

Please don't forget to rate & review!
